prompt.title: Embedding for "Promptbook Ecosystem: Key Tools"
prompt.content: Key tools in the Promptbook ecosystem include **Promptbook Engine** (runs Book applications via NPM/Docker), **Promptbook Studio** (web-based editor/runner), and a **VSCode plugin** for `.book` files.
